.org/blog/ai-transforming-location-based-pet-services</a></li><li>Axios Denver. (2024). <em>Skiptown - a \\\"Disney World for dogs\\\" - opens in Denver</em>. Retrieved from <a href=\\\"https://www.axios.com/local/denver/2024/04/16/skiptown-dog-park-disney-world-summer-opening-denver\\\">axios.com</a></li></ol>\\n<p></p>\\n<p><em>*Last updated: December 2025. Always verify current hours, pricing, vaccination requirements, and policies directly with facilities before visiting. Facility information, pricing, and availability are subject to change.*</em></p>\",\"date\":\"2025-12-17T02:17:02.535Z\",\"modified\":\"2025-12-17T02:52:15Z\",\"author\":{\"id\":57516073,\"name\":\"Indoor Dog Park Directory Team\",\"slug\":\"indoor-dog-park-directory-team\",\"description\":\"Indoor dog park content management team\",\"url\":\"\",\"link\":\"/blog/author/indoor-dog-park-directory-team\",\"avatar_urls\":{\"24\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/f849e70b92252c6a55db9775da309c7f4009a685-2000x832.png?rect=584,0,832,832&w=24&h=24\",\"48\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/f849e70b92252c6a55db9775da309c7f4009a685-2000x832.png?rect=584,0,832,832&w=48&h=48\",\"96\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/f849e70b92252c6a55db9775da309c7f4009a685-2000x832.png?rect=584,0,832,832&w=96&h=96\"}},\"categories\":[{\"id\":83297818,\"name\":\"City Guides\",\"slug\":\"city-guides\",\"description\":\"City Guides\",\"count\":0,\"link\":\"/blog/category/city-guides\",\"taxonomy\":\"category\",\"parent\":0,\"meta\":{}}],\"tags\":[{\"id\":5473141,\"name\":\"Climate control\",\"slug\":\"climate-control\",\"description\":\"\",\"count\":0,\"link\":\"/blog/tag/climate-control\",\"taxonomy\":\"post_tag\",\"meta\":{}},{\"id\":53459804,\"name\":\"indoor dog park\",\"slug\":\"indoor-dog-park\",\"description\":\"\",\"count\":0,\"link\":\"/blog/tag/indoor-dog-park\",\"taxonomy\":\"post_tag\",\"meta\":{}},{\"id\":90100489,\"name\":\"Pets care\",\"slug\":\"pets-care\",\"